         <div type="translation">
            <ab>From [the] apodektai [of the 9th pagus?] to the sitologoi of Philoteris.  [We acknowledge ?] that we have [received?] from Aphrodas ... [   ] artabas of clean wheat including the 10 percent and the denarius per modius.  Year 9 and 7 and 5, Epeiph .., and of barley likewise for the same village, [    art.], that is, [.]7 art. of barley.
</ab>
